flowchart TD
    A["_attribute_chunk(chunk, depth)"] --> B["chat() to parse JSON<br/>drop echoed roster lines"]
    B --> C["coverage = _chunk_coverage(chunk, out)"]
    C --> D{"out empty OR coverage < 0.85 ?<br/>and depth<4 and len>1200"}
